{"tid":448174,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[滅蝗?] 紐西蘭擬禁外國人買二手樓阻樓價攀升","createTime":"2017-10-26T03:45:50.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-26T12:17:38.000Z","uid":77196,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"31155c4dddb06795baae16c9d32aedf28476e021","tid":448174,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T03:45:50.000Z","msg":"紐西蘭新政府計劃禁止外國人在當地購買二手物業，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>且有意削減移民數量，以遏制因為大量移民湧入，而日漸攀升的樓價</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭新任總理阿德恩(Jacinda Ardern)表示，該禁令將僅適用於非紐西蘭居民，強調政府的目標和承諾是禁止外國買家進入二手物業市場。<br />\n<br />\n由於當地低利率、住房庫存有限，加上大量移民湧入，紐西蘭樓價不斷飆升。以往，美國投資者被認為是推動紐西蘭房價上漲的主要因素，<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>但近期中國買家大量湧入，已遠超美國買家</strong></span>。<br />\n<br />\n澳新銀行(ANZ)今年2月估計，紐西蘭的住房短缺已達到6萬套，並且以平均每天40套的速度增長。紐西蘭房地產研究所(REINZ)9月數據顯示，該國最大城市奧克蘭的樓價中位數已達84.5萬紐元(約454.34萬港元)，較2008年11月上漲近一倍。<br />\n<br />\n紐西蘭政府此舉並非首例，早在2011年，澳洲政府推出禁止海外買家購買二手物業的政策，今年3月又禁止外國人購買新樓盤逾半數住宅的政策。"},{"pid":"92da066a242a7cc30e40e32ab7accdcf10896ac4","tid":448174,"uid":70985,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:14:40.000Z","msg":"垃圾香港唔會學下人只限香港永久居民，有交稅先俾買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e03c643f6687df69adcf891f23922e415dde4157","tid":448174,"uid":35790,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T05:29:05.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>垃圾香港唔會學下人只限香港永久居民，有交稅先俾買樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n人地係國家<br />\n香港係支那一國一制城市"},{"pid":"67feee73327d08ed65b0f5ef015b3583a4e1a780","tid":448174,"uid":70985,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:13:58.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4104cd79323ccef7cb179ada295aceaa074e975e","tid":448174,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:16:15.000Z","msg":"冇用, 啲外地炒家開間本地公司就得. 除非話剩係公民加自然人先准買二手樓."},{"pid":"6e7bb29721e54fd87e9a43326d8eb06b8bd3d3f5","tid":448174,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:26:44.000Z","msg":"澳洲已經好撚孤立<br />\n諗唔到點解會移民紐西蘭"},{"pid":"9e5609c7400b4aa90845d41f0520432b8b13bd62","tid":448174,"uid":22858,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T07:40:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"999e20a6ddf511e213744477f4d7f62793414b3c","tid":448174,"uid":75326,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:02:55.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇用, 啲外地炒家開間本地公司就得. 除非話剩係公民加自然人先准買二手樓.</blockquote><br />\n人地定條法律出黎，可以俾你轉插入將翻一軍? <br />\n以為全世界都好撚似班港官呃鳩班港豬一樣?"},{"pid":"37d329fda8a36f7c03b2394f1d3199a793cd346a","tid":448174,"uid":6347,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T08:07:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇用, 啲外地炒家開間本地公司就得. 除非話剩係公民加自然人先准買二手樓.</blockquote><br />\n人地定條法律出黎，可以俾你轉插入將翻一軍? <br />\n以為全世界都好撚似班港官呃鳩班港豬一樣?</blockquote><br />\n而家過去好似一個人要幾百萬"},{"pid":"6c7d208bf92a62ae1ab11a4a4feb2aa0fdb47ebc","tid":448174,"uid":82929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:40:17.000Z","msg":"澳紐咁多地，人口密度咁低<br />\n都唔明點解樓價咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7eccaee273c68999138cf22af36bd15fe9fcd706","tid":448174,"uid":46527,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:41:05.000Z","msg":"香港唔駛諗"},{"pid":"da918778feb29f4c940f56428b3a806841237559","tid":448174,"uid":47359,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:42:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">德政<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> </span></span>"},{"pid":"189b7045fbeb00ccd4c7bd66daa35c7cb2ed6eee","tid":448174,"uid":37735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T09:57:34.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇用, 啲外地炒家開間本地公司就得. 除非話剩係公民加自然人先准買二手樓.</blockquote><br />\n人地定條法律出黎，可以俾你轉插入將翻一軍? <br />\n以為全世界都好撚似班港官呃鳩班港豬一樣?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n人地有選民懲罰呢樣野<br />\n<br />\n做樣定真係做  選民知道 反映係個選票<br />\n<br />\n你估好像支那同香港<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c735a97bd8957517e1cca4c961905540e9c30bb3","tid":448174,"uid":16970,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:07:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇用, 啲外地炒家開間本地公司就得. 除非話剩係公民加自然人先准買二手樓.</blockquote><br />\n人地定條法律出黎，可以俾你轉插入將翻一軍? <br />\n以為全世界都好撚似班港官呃鳩班港豬一樣?</blockquote><br />\n當地大學教授都係咁講.<br />\n<br />\nIn terms of its implementation Massey University associate professor from the school of people, environment and planning Grant Duncan said there would always be grey areas that could make such a policy challenging.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;One thing I heard, was it okay if someone gets approval to buy a farm and there happens to be an existing residential house. How does that fit?<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Who counts as a foreigner? You might be a foreign buyer, but you lend some money to a family member who has permanent residence.<br />\n<br />\n&quot;Those are the questions this new Government has to grapple with and make clear to the public.&quot;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.nzherald.co.nz/business/news/article.cfm?c_id=3&amp;objectid=11937172\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.nzherald.co.nz%2Fbusiness%2Fnews%2Farticle.cfm%3Fc_id%3D3%26objectid%3D11937172&d=myV3ArmkQETIy5dlh0XiuwHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=319668cc\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.nzherald.co.nz/business/news/article.cfm?c_id=3&amp;objectid=11937172</a>"},{"pid":"76c7a57eea8f449b869029749a0895dd658a196c","tid":448174,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:42:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>冇用, 啲外地炒家開間本地公司就得. 除非話剩係公民加自然人先准買二手樓.</blockquote><br />\n澳洲會查公司㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間公司非澳洲藉股東hold多過20%已經要同政府申請"},{"pid":"cd1014a7d8d28846a482bca227c1eed3fddc7dd3","tid":448174,"uid":13724,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:42:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳紐咁多地，人口密度咁低<br />\n都唔明點解樓價咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n因為啲人堆晒喺幾點"},{"pid":"93aad2f0d65d4f54227847620c353d2b82c244a9","tid":448174,"uid":476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T10:45:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>澳紐咁多地，人口密度咁低<br />\n都唔明點解樓價咁高<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n叫cc台搬入屯門都要你去死咁啦 又交通唔方便又話有牛 <br />\n你又問人點解唔住遠d？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ede1736454269cb9561d2043b8a0ba2035d3af59","tid":448174,"uid":17103,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-26T12:17:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>冇用, 啲外地炒家開間本地公司就得. 除非話剩係公民加自然人先准買二手樓.</blockquote><br />\n澳洲會查公司㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 間公司非澳洲藉股東hold多過20%已經要同政府申請</blockquote><br />\n20 一個人或者 40 總共"}]}